item.title: Opinion towards Liberal and gender
item.description: Abstract “In this paper we analysed the 2019 CES phone survey data. By analyzing the data, the results showed that females have more positive opinion towards Liberal in Canada. These results are important because it gives a forecast people’s behavior in the election and can give a positive impact on the party’s campaign strategy.” Introduction In Canada, the difference political opinion among genders have been extended in the last election.
